  "monster": {
    "title": "Ubetayri.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Ubetayri has a tentacled light blue body and a hideous tangle of tentacles for a mouth.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 157     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ +++  </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ++.     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ∞        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 140% (normally travels slower than you)\n\nYou have about 20% to hit with the earth staff of Heof.\nIt has about 22% to hit you.\n\nAttack    Max Damage  \nTentacle  54          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting Ubetayri.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Fast:<lightgrey>\n   This creature moves and acts 50% faster.\n\n<white>Sheltered from injuries:<lightgrey>\n   Half of the damage suffered by this creature is redirected to the ally\n   protecting it instead.\n\n<white>Lightly drained:<lightgrey>\n   This creature has been lightly drained, somewhat lowering the accuracy of\n   their melee attacks, the power of their spells and special attack properties,\n   and making them slightly more vulnerable to many status effects.\n\n",
